high_descs: Turn right and walk to the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the small square table to the left of the dresser.
Place the glass on the small table, to the right of the book.
anns.task_desc: Place a glass on a table.

high_descs: Go to the coffee table to your right.
Pick up the gold decoration on the table.
Turn to your left and go to the small end table across from you.
Place the gold decoration on the right, front corner of the end table.
anns.task_desc: Put a gold decoration on the end table.

high_descs: turn to the right to face the coffee table
pick up the gold jar with the lid from the coffee table
turn to the left and move to the small table with the book on it
put the gold jar on to the small table to the right of the book
anns.task_desc: put the gold jar on to the small table
